<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n25200j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n25" href="#n25200j">N25 (VI.B.15)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n25all.htm#n25200j"> 200(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> prophecy sleep with drum</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Their magicians prophesied by means of a drum, on which they painted the images of the gods and of things about which inquiry was made; having slept with this under his head, the magician on awaking told what he had seen in his dreams. <small> Frank Vincent, <a name="FVNLF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FVNLF"><cite title="source">Norsk, Lapp, and Finn</cite></a> (1881) 148</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c14138j" href="c14all.htm#c14138j">VI.C.14:138(j)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
